{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "本章题为\"夺命之剑\"。慕容秋荻深夜来到谢晓峰身边，指出他因恐惧燕十三而紧张，并透露自己曾想亲手杀死谢晓峰却被段十三所救。段十三是一位拥有十三把刀却专司救人的神秘刀客，因畏惧燕十三而不敢露面。谢晓峰释然，因他一直怀疑段十三救他是为了与他一较高下。慕容秋荻坦言自己仍爱着谢晓峰，又提起他们的儿子——谢晓峰若能击败燕十三，她便带儿子来认父。谢晓峰坦承对燕十三的第十四剑有破解之法，却指出夺命十三剑的真正精粹在于尚未出现的第十五剑——如花朵绽放般才是剑法的终极。若第十五剑现世，天下无人能敌。谢晓峰宁死也愿目睹此剑法。章末场景转至月下扁舟上的神秘老人（燕十三），他以桃木削成木剑，一气呵成刺出十三剑、第十四剑，最终在第十五剑中达到\"死\"的境界——万物终结，木剑断裂。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我看不出，可是我知道，你若不紧张，怎么会看上那个眼睛像死鱼一样的女人？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我想不到你为什么会如此紧张。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你也有想不到的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "也许我已经想到了，只不过不愿意相信而已。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我一向很了解你，只有害怕才会让你紧张。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我怕什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你怕败在别人的剑下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为谢家的三少爷是永远不能败的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 19
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是这世上能威胁到你的人并不多，也许只有一个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 25,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "燕十三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你怎么知道这次就是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我当然知道，就因为你是谢晓峰，他是燕十三，你们两个人就迟早总有相见的一天，迟早总有一个人要死在对方的剑下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这就是你们的命运，谁都没法子改变的，连我都没法子改变。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我本来很想要你死在我手里，想不到还是有个人救了你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你知道那个人是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果我早就知道世上有他这么样一个人，我早就杀了他。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在我虽然知道了，却已太迟了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "现在你已经知道他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他叫段十三，他有十三把刀，却是救命的刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我怎么从来没有听说过这个人？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为燕十三要杀他，只要燕十三活着，他就不敢露面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "现在我总算放心了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "放什么心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我一直在怀疑他就是燕十三，他救我，只因为要跟我一较高下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是他偏偏又救了你的命，你怎么能让他死在你的剑下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 65,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你担心的若是这一点，那么你现在就真的可以放心了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我知道燕十三绝不是你的敌手，你一定可以杀了他的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "你到这里来，就是为了要让我放心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 71,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我到这里来，只因为我还是喜欢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "有时候我虽然也恨你，恨不得要你死，可是别人想碰一碰你，我都会生气，你要死也得死在我手里。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "我只想找个地方好好的睡一觉去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你不睡在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "有你在旁边，我睡不着！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "因为我也不想死在你手里，至少现在还不想。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天你可以安心睡在这里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算我以前曾经恨不得要你死，可是今天我不想，至少今天并不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "难道今天是个很特别的日子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 107,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "今天的日子并不特别好，却有个特别的人来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你应该记得我们还有个儿子。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "他也来了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是我带他来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "现在他的人呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他并不知道你在这里，你也绝不会找到他的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算找到了又有什么用？难道你不知道他恨你，恨你从来没有把他当作自己的儿子，从来没有尽到做父亲的责任。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "难道现在你已有勇气告诉他，你就是他的父亲？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是你只要能击败燕十三，我就会带他来见你，而你可以告诉他，你就是他的父亲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "一个男孩子如果永远不知道自己的父亲是谁，不但他一定会痛苦终生，他的母亲也一样痛苦。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "所以你也一直都没有让他知道，你就是他的亲生母亲？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我没有！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是现在我年纪已渐渐大了，我想要的，大多数都已得到，现在我只想能够有个儿子，像他那样的儿子。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "难道你已决心将所有的事全都告诉他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 147
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我甚至还会告诉他，你并没有错，错的是我。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "既然，你已下了决心，为什么又要等到我击败燕十三之后才告诉他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为你若不胜，就只有死。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若死在燕十三剑下，我又何必让他知道自己有这么样一个父亲？又何必再增加他的烦恼和痛苦？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我又何必再让他去送死？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "送死？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "他若知道自己的父亲是死在燕十三剑下的，当然要去复仇，他又怎能会是燕十三的敌手？不是去送死是什么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我相信你当然不会败的，你自己也应该很有把握。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "这一次我没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "难道连你都破不了他的夺命十三剑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "夺命十三剑并不可怕，可怕的是第十四剑。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪里还有第十四剑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是说他的夺命十三剑，还有第十四种变化？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算真的有，只怕连他自己都不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "就算他以前不知道，现在也一定知道了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是我相信这第十四剑，也未必能胜你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "不错，他也未必能胜我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我想你说不定已有了破他这一剑的方法。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我想你现在就已有了破他这十四剑的方法。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你用不着瞒我，你瞒不过我的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 229,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "不错，我可以破他这一剑，只可惜……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "还可惜什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "可惜这一剑还不是他剑法中真正的精粹。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "这一剑还不是？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "绝不是。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么他剑法中真正的精粹是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "是第十五剑！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "明明是夺命十三剑，怎么会又有第十五剑？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "他这套剑法精深微妙，绝对还应该有第十五种变化，那就像是……像是……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "像是什么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "就像是一株花。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "前面的十三剑，只不过是花的根而已，第十四剑，也只不过是些枝叶，一定要等到有了第十五种变化时，鲜花才会开放，他的第十五剑，才是真正的花朵。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "夺命十三剑也一样，若没有第十五剑，这套剑法根本就全无价值。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "如果有了第十五剑又怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "那时非但我不是他的对手，天下也绝没有任何人会是他的对手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那时你就必将死在他的剑下？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "text": "只要能看到世上有那样的剑法出现，我纵然死在他的剑下，死亦无憾！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_qiu_di",
      "speaker_name": "慕容秋荻",
      "listener": "char_xiao_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在燕十三是不是已创出了这一剑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    }
  ],
